            "question": "Can I use it with a CPAP mask?",
            "answer": "<p>Dreamtape is designed for people who breathe well through their nose without extra equipment. If you use a CPAP or another sleep therapy device, check with your healthcare provider before combining it with mouth tape.</p>"
          }
        },
